<Class name="CM_MoveServiceBroker" id="1419430d-80d6-42ae-981e-2c4801466abd">
    <superclass name="CM_ServiceBroker"/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>The Persistant TI Transaction Map, as in CM_TiTransaction,  for TRACKEDITEM transaction map.

Cargo – CM_Bank.transactionMaps
   Transaction Map – CM_TranMap.allTIServices (these are the cargo type mapping)
      Cargo Type – CM_TIServiceMap.allProductGroupMaps (the cargo sub type group mappings)
		Cargo Subtype Group - CM_ProductGroupMap.allProductMaps (the cargo sub type mappings)
			Cargo Subtype - CM_ProductMap.allImExMaps (then imex status mappings)
				ImEx Status – CM_imexServiceMap.contentsMap
					Contents Status – CM_ContentsMap.commoditiesMap
If Move transaction then
						Commodity – CM_CommodityMap.moveMap - 
							Move - CM_MoveServiceBroker.allDebtorMapsByDebtor &lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt; YOU ARE HERE
	If has specific debtor mapping then
								Debtor - CM_DebtorMap.myChildQuantityMap
									Quantity Map - CM_QuantityMap.allQuantityRanges
										QuantityRange - CM_QuantityRangeMap.allInvoiceLineMaps
											Invoice Line - CM_InvoiceLineDesc
	else no specific debtor mapping
							Move - CM_MoveServiceBroker.myChildQuantityMap &lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt; YOU ARE HERE
								Quantity Map - CM_QuantityMap.allQuantityRanges
									QuantityRange - CM_QuantityRangeMap.allInvoiceLineMaps
										Invoice Line - CM_InvoiceLineDesc							
							
else all other transaction types
						Commodity – CM_CommodityMap.allTransServiceBrokersByType
							Transaction (ServiceBroker)
							
	If has specific debtor mapping then
							Transaction (ServiceBroker) - CM_TransServiceBroker.allDebtorMapsByDebtor 
								Debtor - CM_DebtorMap.myChildQuantityMap
									Quantity Map - CM_QuantityMap.allQuantityRanges
										QuantityRange - CM_QuantityRangeMap.allInvoiceLineMaps
											Invoice Line - CM_InvoiceLineDesc
	else no specific debtor mapping
							Transaction (ServiceBroker) - CM_TransServiceBroker.myChildQuantityMap 
								Quantity Map - CM_QuantityMap.allQuantityRanges
									QuantityRange - CM_QuantityRangeMap.allInvoiceLineMaps
										Invoice Line - CM_InvoiceLineDesc
</text>
    <DbClassMap file="invoice"/>
